install_command: cd libs/langchain && pip install -e . &&  cd - && wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.9.6/Python-3.9.6.tgz && tar xzf Python-3.9.6.tgz && cd Python-3.9.6 && ./configure --enable-optimizations --prefix=/opt/python/python3.9.6 && make -j$(nproc) && make altinstall && ln -s /opt/python/python3.9.6/bin/python3.9 /usr/local/bin/python3.9.6 && cd .. && rm -rf Python-3.9.6.tgz Python-3.9.6
